< Knife
	It will cut your lifestream.
	
>

I. Given to Protagonist by Alchemist
II. Mechanics
 A. Leaves glowing mark after succesful hit
  1. Only mark on surfaces that can be marked
		ie: No marks on concrete walls
  2. Can be used to show where protagonist has been
 B. Weapon
  1. Minor Damage
  2. No real confrontation value
		ie: will lose in a straight foreward 1-on-1 fight
